  🚀 Quick Start

  1. Install Dependencies

  cd /Users/ken/clawd_workspace/projects/KG_RAG/v1.0-beta/web_ui_vite

  # With npm
  npm install

  # Or with Bun (faster)
  bun install

  2. Start Development Server

  npm run dev
  # or
  bun run dev

  Features:

  • 🔄 Hot Module Replacement - Instant updates on file change
  • 🎯 TypeScript checking - Catch errors before runtime
  • 🌐 API Proxy - Automatically forwards /api to localhost:8002

  3. Build for Production

  npm run build

  Output in dist/ folder with:

  • Minified JS/CSS
  • Source maps
  • Optimized chunks

